{"tid":1991873,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同居遇着個死𡃁仔","createTime":"2020-04-27T18:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T07:10:44.000Z","uid":74214,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f07d1a0a769dcc6054938d052abc66cd96cf0671","tid":1991873,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:46:19.000Z","msg":"話說最近工作需要，要同個𡃁仔同住同一屋簷下。<br />\n<br />\n條撚樣打乞嗤唔摭口，就算摭完又唔洗手，返到屋企周圍攤，唔即刻沖涼同換衫先。又唔識拖地，次次用完個廚房成地水，濕笠笠。洗碗唔用洗潔精，求其沖兩沖就算，啲碗拎上手油嘅，屌你老母。<br />\n<br />\n已經有提咗個死𡃁仔好多次，叫佢改善，條撚樣聽完就算，當我耳邊風。<br />\n<br />\n返到自己屋企，阿妹啲嘢又周圍擺，叫佢執兩執又嫌我煩。<br />\n<br />\n成日聽人講相見好同住難，終於都明。"},{"pid":"1ab0c0b981a4045e586845d8040a706cb23cdd5b","tid":1991873,"uid":74214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQoLRcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQoLRcb.jpg&h=3f178768&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dpzGpxc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdpzGpxc.jpg&h=a863ee9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POJ4niT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOJ4niT.jpg&h=442da2d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ojBQ2iU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FojBQ2iU.jpg&h=5f3380ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39087dbcdcace3bf76fac35fcca06c1c0e1eaba5","tid":1991873,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:48:06.000Z","msg":"你同個靚仔有冇扑到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f8d59e3da3f259a5c723025cf312482bc02c5f","tid":1991873,"uid":303133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T18:49:14.000Z","msg":"相見好同住難 完全明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /